parameters: \nc<Saki>Looks like my job offer got revoked again...

\nc<Saki>As expected, it's tough to find a job related to my major.
Everyone freaks out as soon as they hear I've become a
succubus.
\nc<Saki>But I need to find a job as soon as possible...
\nc<Saki>I'm really about to run out of money for food...

\nc<Police>Ah, is this Kiwami-san? Regarding the incident you reported
the other day...

\nc<Police>Upon reviewing the security footage... it appears that the
demon who served you alcohol under the guise of service was
not the manager.

\nc<Saki>What?! I didn't notice at all! (Demons all look alike, so
it's hard to tell...)

\nc<Police>For now, we will continue the investigation, but... did you
really become a succubus?

\nc<Saki>Didn't I show you my tail last time?! Please catch the
culprit at all costs! (I need to catch them to understand
what happened...)
\nc<Saki>Ugh, at this rate, I'm really going to starve to death!
\bustMsgExpression[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Hm? An interview... they're asking me to come?

\nc<Saki>"Succubus First Industries," huh? That's a notoriously black
company, isn't it? I've heard of it. \bustMsgExpression[1,1]

\bustMsgExpression[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Succubus Industries... It's a bit worrying, but since I'm
getting rejected everywhere else based on my resume...

\bustMsgExpression[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Ugh, I'd rather face a black company's interview than die of
hunger. I'm a girl who can do it if I try, so things have to
work out somehow!
